These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, weightlifting, snowboarding, ice-hockey, climbing
5 different games are played: snooker, canasta, mah-jongg, monopoly, chess
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
7. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | snowboarding | skiing | climbing | ice-hockey |
| Game   | chess    | snooker | mah-jongg     | monopoly       | canasta  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different nationalities: turkish, dutch, malaysian, japanese, nigerian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, water-polo, handball, parkour
1. the japanese is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the turkish is in the middle##1
5. the dutch is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is the nigerian##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Nationality      | dutch | malaysian | turkish | japanese | nigerian |
| Sport   | water-polo  | handball   | skateboarding       | cricket    | parkour   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, zombie, horror, martial-arts, action
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, juice, tea, lemonade
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Movie-Genre        | horror | martial-arts | zombie | comedy | action |
| Beverage   | cola  | hot-chocolate      | lemonade | juice | tea      |

