.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different games are played: whist, go, monopoly, snooker, poker
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, chinese, american, british
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the american is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person playing go is on the right of the british##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the chinese is on the far right##1
7. the british is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Game   | snooker    | whist        | monopoly | go | poker |
| Nationality     | australian | american | british  | indonesian   | chinese |

