.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
City: marseilles, nizza, san-francisco, liverpool, new-york
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, paramedic, writer, scientist, lawyer
1. the scientist is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the paramedic is the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the writer is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the writer is in the middle##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the lawyer is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| City    | san-francisco   | marseilles     | nizza   | liverpool         | new-york |
| Job   | nurse | scientist | writer | lawyer | paramedic     |

