.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, 7up, milk, cola
City: venice, marseilles, hannover, london, colone
1. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Beverage       | milk   | 7up   | soy-milk | cola | lemonade |
| City   | marseilles | hannover | london   | colone | venice       |

