.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, purple, mauve, chestnut, green
There 5 different types of food: apricot, grapefruit, cherry, onion, pineapple
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the person eating apricot is the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is in the middle##1
6. the person eating cherry is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Color     | purple   | mauve  | green      | fuchsia | chestnut     |
| Food   | onion | cherry | grapefruit | apricot   | pineapple |

