.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
5 different games are played: billiard, bridge, canasta, backgammon, poker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, electronic, classical, disco
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Game     | bridge | billiard       | poker | backgammon | canasta    |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | disco | electronic  | metal     | hip-hop |

