.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, western, zombie, scientific, documentary
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, lavender, red, yellow, light-blue
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is the person who likes lavender##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | fantasy | zombie | documentary | western |
| Color   | red       | yellow   | light-blue         | lavender   | azure   |

