.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, snowboarding, climbing, badminton
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, house, funk, hip-hop, pop
1. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Sport   | badminton | climbing | sailing | snowboarding | biathlon |
| Music-Genre           | pop      | house    | hip-hop  | salsa     | funk     |

