.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
House: townhouse, tower, wooden, cottage, colonial
5 different games are played: poker, scrabble, monopoly, mah-jongg, whist
1. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing scrabble is the cottage house##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the colonial house is on the far right##1
6. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing poker##1
7. the person playing whist is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| House   | cottage | townhouse  | wooden | tower | colonial |
| Game    | scrabble    | mah-jongg | whist   | poker       | monopoly        |

