.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, pop, trance, reggae, punk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, prince, bongani, aristoff, old-henry
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
2. the fan of reggae is the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the fan of pop##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Music-Genre    | rock | reggae          | trance    | punk | pop  |
| Cigar   | bongani  | old-henry | blend | aristoff | prince |

