.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse, rugby, rowing, cycling
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, august, february, november, september
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Sport   | rugby | parkour      | rowing | lacrosse | cycling |
| Birthday     | november  | august | july     | september     | february  |

