.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, may, january, december, june
5 different games are played: go, bridge, snooker, canasta, billiard
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Birthday      | june | january | august      | december | may      |
| Game   | bridge  | canasta       | go | billiard  | snooker |

