.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, woodworking, cooking, singing, puzzles
5 different games are played: bridge, canasta, scrabble, go, backgammon
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Hobby           | singing     | puzzles | magic-tricks | cooking  | woodworking |
| Game   | bridge | backgammon               | canasta     | scrabble | go |

