.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, alhambra, oliveros, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, september, november, august, october
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
4. the prince-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Cigar   | prince   | alhambra    | tiparillo | oliveros   | bluemaster |
| Birthday     | september | april | august | november | october    |

