.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, fuchsia, chestnut, lilac, white
5 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, backgammon, snooker, bridge
1. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes blue is the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person who likes white is the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Color   | fuchsia   | lilac  | blue | white | chestnut  |
| Game         | scrabble | backgammon | snooker  | bridge    | mah-jongg |

