4. the siglo-smoker is the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the game-smoker##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | time-travel       | martial-arts     | comedy  | satire  |
| Cigar      | bolivar | alhambra | baccarat | game | siglo |

