.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, pop, classical
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, 7up, sprite, almond-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of classical##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | house | classical | indie | folk | pop |
| Beverage           | almond-milk | sprite  | hot-chocolate    | mirinda  | 7up   |

 